04:07.622 --> 04:09.124
oh, what's a good number--

04:09.166 --> 04:11.085
275 bars.

04:11.126 --> 04:12.961
Looks like there's

04:11.126 --> 04:12.961
about another half hour

04:13.003 --> 04:15.172
of sunlight left--

04:13.003 --> 04:15.172
what are you waiting for?

04:15.214 --> 04:16.506
Fine, I'll do it!

04:16.548 --> 04:18.299
But I just want

04:16.548 --> 04:18.299
