07:52.597 --> 07:55.100
You know. People.

07:52.597 --> 07:55.100
People who don't have

07:55.142 --> 07:57.518
this country's best interests

07:55.142 --> 07:57.518
at heart.

07:57.560 --> 08:01.398
So, these candy bars

07:57.560 --> 08:01.398
help fight terrorism?

08:01.440 --> 08:05.026
With every chocolatey,

08:01.440 --> 08:05.026
