08:05.068 --> 08:05.902
How much are they?

08:05.944 --> 08:08.029
$9.50.

08:08.071 --> 08:09.114
I'll take two.

08:09.156 --> 08:10.031
Thank you.

08:10.073 --> 08:11.950
