10:39.931 --> 10:40.932
Wait a minute.

10:40.974 --> 10:43.268
It seems to me if Reese

10:40.974 --> 10:43.268
fixed your experiment,

10:43.310 --> 10:44.519
he should get some credit.

10:44.561 --> 10:46.146
What? No.

10:46.187 --> 10:47.981
He doesn't even know

10:46.187 --> 10:47.981
why it works.

10:48.022 --> 10:50.191
I've been working for 20 years

10:48.022 --> 10:50.191
without knowing why.

10:50.233 --> 10:52.360
Give Reese the credit.

